desc_long							评测						“A game of art, a game of immersion, a game of challenges and above all lots of fun!”Indie Retro News“One of the most fascinating games I've seen this year”Indie Game News												关于这款游戏							For a long, long time they have been bound by rules and assumptions. Trapped within the boundaries of signs. Until one day, the kid from the school crossing sign is thrown out – unleashing a new world – the world of Sign Motion. Where will the kid go now? Will others follow, help or oppose?Experience mind-bending puzzles in a strange yet familiar world.						
